      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "**Structural alerts relevant to hERG**\n- **\u201cBasic center + flanking aromatics/hydrophobes\u201d** pattern is strongly present.\n- **Piperidine/piperazine-type cationic ring + aromatic domains** is a classic hERG liability motif.\n- **Terfenadine-like** in the sense of a **large lipophilic diaryl region** connected through a **flexible chain** to a **basic center** (not identical, but pharmacophore-similar).",
      "tool_name": null,
